  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Food and drinks stall assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Core Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Customer Service & Sales:</strong> Greeting customers, taking orders, handling cash or digital payments (POS system), and managing takeaway packaging.</li><li><strong>Food/Drink Preparation:</strong> Preparing beverages (coffee, tea, drinks), simple food items (toasting, reheating, basic cooking), and ensuring quality.</li><li><strong>Stall Hygiene & Cleaning:</strong> Cleaning work areas, equipment, crockery, and cutlery to maintain food safety standards.</li><li><strong>Operations & Inventory:</strong> Monitoring stock levels of ingredients and supplies, restocking displays, and assisting with opening/closing routines.</li><li><strong>Service & Support:</strong> Serving food to tables, assisting managers, and performing ad-hoc duties as needed. </li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Willingness to learn, good attitude, and ability to work in a fast-paced environment.</li><li>Knowledge of food safety/hygiene regulations is usually required. </li></ul>",
